name: Warung Semur (Serba Murah)
description: E-Commerce for digital-based MSMEs that accommodates micro-economic activities between sellers and buyers. In this system, sellers can market their products and buyers can make transactions.

name: e-Library
description: A web application that allows users to search for books and read them. The application also allows admin to add books to their library. This system is designed to meet the needs of e-book publishing.

name: SIOTANG
description: This project aims to make ask-for-hand-signature in formalities & bureaucracy easier during pandemics. Basically this is an information system for signing the approval sheet for industrial work practice proposals. Built for Electrical Engineering UM.

name: Fruit Parcel AI (Knapsack)
description: This project aims to solve the problem of finding the best combination of fruits to maximize the profit. The project is built using Dart and Flutter. The project is based on BFS algorithm for knapsack problem.

name: Mulyotani
description: A simple landing page to promote automatic bird repellent device called "Mulyotani". So that rice plants can thrive and be free from pests.

name: Burger
description: A simple burger web application that allows users to order burgers using drag and drop mechanism. The project is built using Javascript Drag Events.

name: E-Brent
description: An online and android application-based bicycle rental application to make it easier for people who want to use electric bicycles. This app is built using flutter and firebase.

name: Smart School
description: A private projects or ecosystem about multi-apps that connected via single login SAML. This projects aims to digitalize school system.
